This folder contains TRSs with integer constraints in the LCTRS ARI format ( https://project-coco.uibk.ac.at/ARI/lctrs.php ).

The TRSs in the files
 - pro_circuit.ari
 - perm_circuit.ari
correspond to the TRSs described in figures 2 and 4 in the paper:

"Towards Term-based Verification of Diagrammatic Equivalence" 
by Julie Cailler , Noé Delorme , Simon Perdrix , Sophie Tourret, 
included in the proceedings of IJCAR 2026 (not yet available at the time this README was created).

The paper is available on arXiv at: https://arxiv.org/abs/2602.11035 .